<p>
	The change is to move the team to a service based culture through training, leadership and advocacy,
	implement an ITIL compliant management tool and wrap a process around the tool that supports ITIL
	to gain the first level of benefits of good service management espoused by ITIL aficionados.
</p>

<p>
	You will see

	<ul>
